eviously thought. These adjustments can be accommodated easily, and, in fact,\nbring the Local Bubble's pressure more in line with that of the adjacent\nmaterial. Suggestions for future work are made.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Apr 2008 17:53:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-06-23"}
