nce at a lower feedback rate than existing schemes\nin which the detection order is fed back to the transmitter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Apr 2008 19:55:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 15 Apr 2008 20:08:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-04-16"}
